<html><head>
<style>
.button {
    background: #26BF12;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #45637E;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    padding: 9px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 10px 15px;
}
</style>
</head><body><div id="content-container" style="width:640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
  <div id="content-body" style="padding: 20px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #dddddd; border-radius: 3px; line-height: 2em; font-family: Arial">
    <p>Forgot your password, {{fullname}}? No problem!</p>
    <p>To set a new password, click on the link below (or copy and paste the URL into your browser):<br><a href="{{reset_password_url}}">{{reset_password_url}}</a></p>
    <p><b>Why did I get this email?</b></p>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account ({{username}}).</p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset you can just delete this email. Your password will not be changed.</p>
  </div>
  {% include "emails/footer.html" %}
</div></body></html>
